Business Brief -- Dell Computer Corp.:
   Firm Says BancTec Agrees
   To Offer 3rd-Party Services
For an additional fee, BancTec will promise to arrive
on-site within four hours in 17 major metropolitan areas.
Dell has traditionally offered next-day maintenance service
through Xerox, which last year announced it was exiting from
the third-party service business.
   BancTec Inc., Dallas, provides integrated financial
transaction processing systems, application software and
support services, largely for the financial services
industry.